min_value = np.inf
for a in itertools.combinations(df,2):
    if np.sum((df.loc[:,a[0]]-df.loc[:,a[1]])**2)<min_value:
        min_value = np.sum((df.loc[:,a[0]]-df.loc[:,a[1]])**2)
        ticker = a
        print(min_value)
        print(ticker)
print('min:{}'.format(min_value))
